### Health
GET http://localhost:8000/health

### Routes summary
GET http://localhost:8000/routes

### Delay by route
GET http://localhost:8000/delay?route_id=1

### Delay by route and vehicle type
GET http://localhost:8000/delay?route_id=1&vehicle_type=bus

### Global stats
GET http://localhost:8000/stats

### Heatmap aggregate
GET http://localhost:8000/heatmap

### Top routes defaults
GET http://localhost:8000/top-routes

### Top routes with filters
GET http://localhost:8000/top-routes?limit=5&min_events=200
